sentence: The war cry for justice was all over - Much to the chagrin of the authorities.
Albanian: Thirrja e luftës për drejtësi ishte e gjitha - shumë për zhgënjimin e autoriteteve.
backtrans: The call for justice was all - much about the frustration of the authorities.

sentence: The regime's decision adumbrates the underlying agenda.
Albanian: Vendimi i regjimit ndryshon axhendën themelore.
backtrans: The regime's decision varies the basic agenda.

sentence: The community was anxious over the passing of the much needed reforms.
Albanian: Komuniteti ishte i shqetësuar për kalimin e reformave shumë të nevojshme.
backtrans: The community was concerned about passing the necessary reforms.

sentence: The think tank  published a paper outlining their apology of capital punishment.
Albanian: Think Tank publikoi një letër që përshkruante faljen e tyre të dënimit me vdekje.
backtrans: Think Tank published a letter depicting their pardon of death penalty.

sentence: Aught was left of the petition's validity
Albanian: Aught kishte mbetur nga vlefshmëria e peticionit
backtrans: Aught was left of the validity of the petition

sentence: The President exhorted his ministers to buckle up as key opposition support for his economic plan was about to buckle.
Albanian: Presidenti nxiti ministrat e tij që të shtrëngonin si mbështetje kryesore të opozitës për planin e tij ekonomik ishte gati të shtrëngohej.
backtrans: The president urged his ministers to tighten as the main support of the opposition for his economic plan was about to constrain.

sentence: The voters were chuffed to see the bill passed.
Albanian: Votuesit u përplasën për të parë faturën e kaluar.
backtrans: Voters crashed to see the bill last.

sentence: The lawyer's discursive narration swayed the jury.
Albanian: Tregimi diskursor i avokatit lëkundi jurinë.
backtrans: The discourse story of the lawyer rocking the jury.

sentence: The EU block opposed an eventual imposition of anti-dumping measures.
Albanian: Blloku i BE kundërshtoi një vendosje eventuale të masave antidumping.
backtrans: The EU block objected to an eventual placement of anti-dumping measures.

sentence: A fulsome eulogy was delivered by the sly counsel.
Albanian: Një eulogy i plotë u dorëzua nga këshilla e zymtë.
backtrans: A complete eulogy was delivered by gloomy tips.

sentence: The gig-economy agency decided to garnish the refunds!
Albanian: Agjencia e Gig-Ekonomisë vendosi të garnizojë rimbursimet!
backtrans: The GIG-Economics Agency decided to garrison refunds!

sentence: Members of the anti-theocratic revolutionary movement overthrew the peers in power!
Albanian: Anëtarët e lëvizjes revolucionare anti -okratike përmbysën kolegët në pushtet!
backtrans: Members of the Revolutionary Anti-Regricity Movement overthrew the ruling colleagues!

sentence: The traitors disappointingly decided to fight with the colonialists.
Albanian: Tradhët vendosën zhgënjyese për të luftuar me kolonialistët.
backtrans: Traitors disappointed to fight with colonialists.
